Package: flowtype
Version: 1.4.4
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-venv, python3-pip, ydotool, wl-clipboard, xdotool, portaudio19-dev, ffmpeg, libxcb-cursor0
Maintainer: Victor <victor@localhost>
Description: Voice dictation for Ubuntu 24/25 (Wayland + X11)
 Hold Right Shift (or configure any hotkey) to record voice, release to
 transcribe and type. Supports Wayland (ydotool) and X11 (xdotool).
 Uses faster-whisper for offline speech recognition.
